'''加雲·安祖·賀迪'''（{{lang-en|'''Gavin Andrew Hoyte'''}}，{{bd|1990年|6月6日|catIdx=Hoyte, Gavin}}），是一名在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生的[[特立尼达和多巴哥共和國|千里達]][[足球員|足球員]]，出身[[英超|英超]]球隊[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]青訓系統，司職[[後衛_(足球)|後衛]]，多擔任[[中堅|中堅]]。

他是[[賈斯汀·賀迪|賈斯汀·賀迪]]的弟弟，其兄在2008年轉會[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]之前，曾為阿仙奴的邊後衛。他們的母親雲迪·賀迪（Wendy Hoyte，嫁夫前名為雲迪·奇勒）是[[英國|英國]]50米室內[[短跑|短跑]]紀錄保持者。

==生平==
加雲·賀迪於年僅9歲時已經效力[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]<small><ref name="contract">{{cite news |url=http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/gavin-hoyte-signs-new-long-term-contract |title=Gavin-hoyte-signs-new-long-term-contract |publisher=Arsenal.com |date=2008-12-16 |accessdate=2009-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210052922/http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/gavin-hoyte-signs-new-long-term-contract |archivedate=2009-02-10 }}</ref></small>，在阿仙奴U18和預備隊表現突出，於2006/07年球季為阿仙奴U18的隊長<small><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.thefa.com/England/U17WorldCup/NewsFeatures/Postings/WorldCupEngGermanyHoyte.htm | title=Running in the family | work=TheFA.com | date=2007-09-02 | accessdate=2009-02-28 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081209022738/http://www.thefa.com/England/U17WorldCup/NewsFeatures/Postings/WorldCupEngGermanyHoyte.htm | archivedate=2008-12-09 }}</ref></small>。2007年9月10日和球會簽訂職業合約<small><ref name="profile">{{cite web |url=http://www.arsenal.com/reserves-youth/players/gavin-hoyte |title=Gavin Hoyte |work=Arsenal.com |accessdate=2007-10-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219044339/http://www.arsenal.com/reserves-youth/players/gavin-hoyte |archivedate=2008-12-19 }}</ref></small>。他亦是[[英格蘭17歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U17]]的隊員，曾入選[[2007年世界少年足球錦標賽|2007年世少盃]]英格蘭大軍。他在該項賽事合共替英格蘭上陣全部五場賽事，當中對戰[[巴西U17|巴西U17]]和[[德國U17|德國U17]]正選上場，其餘三場皆後備上陣<small><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/statisticsandrecords/players/player=274119/index.html | title=Gavin HOYTE | work=[[FIFA|FIFA]].com | date= | accessdate=2009-02-28 | archive-date=2014-01-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140112231539/http://www.fifa.com/worldfootball/statisticsandrecords/players/player=274119/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

自2007年開始，加雲·賀迪偶爾被阿仙奴選進一隊，以填滿後備名單，坐在後備席上沒有上場；首次是2007年2月28日[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第五輪重賽對[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]<small><ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/6397551.stm | title=Blackburn 1-0 Arsenal | work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date=2007-02-28 | accessdate=2009-02-28 | archive-date=2008-12-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207035214/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/6397551.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。其後在2007/08年球季五場阿仙奴的[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]賽事，他被選進了名單四次，對手分別是[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]<small><ref name="cc_newcastle">{{cite web | url=http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/wenger-names-squad-for-carling-cup-tie | title=Wenger names squad for Carling Cup tie | work=Arsenal.com | date= | accessdate=2009-02-28 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205052827/http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/wenger-names-squad-for-carling-cup-tie | archivedate=2008-12-05 }}</ref></small>、[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]<small><ref name="cc_shefutd">{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7065196.stm | title=Sheff Utd 0-3 Arsenal | work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date=2007-10-31 | accessdate=2009-02-28 | archive-date=2009-03-12 | archive-url=https://swap.stanford.edu/20090312234408/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7065196.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref></small>、[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]<small><ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7145781.stm | title=Blackburn 2-3 Arsenal (aet) | work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date=2007-12-18 | accessdate=2009-02-28 | archive-date=2009-02-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210194914/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7145781.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref></small>和[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|托定咸熱刺]]<small><ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7172903.stm | title=Arsenal 1-1 Tottenham | work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport | date=2008-01-09 | accessdate=2009-02-28 | archive-date=2009-03-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327054257/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7172903.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但四場皆沒有上陣。

賀迪在阿仙奴2008年季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]踢了兩場一隊賽事，在2008/09年球季被任命為預備隊隊長<small><ref name="profile"/></small>。他終在2008年9月23日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]首次為阿仙奴一隊上陣對[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|錫菲聯]]，以正選右閘踢足全場90分鐘，結果阿仙奴大勝對手6-0<small><ref name="pro">{{cite web | url=http://www.arsenal.com/match-menu/3060510/first-team/arsenal-v-sheff-utd?tab=report | title=Arsenal 6-0 Sheff United | work=Arsenal.com | date=2008-09-23 | accessdate=2009-02-28 | archive-date=2009-02-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090217065300/http://www.arsenal.com/match-menu/3060510/first-team/arsenal-v-sheff-utd?tab=report | dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他在聯賽盃下兩輪對[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]和[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]亦有上陣，他亦在2008年11月22日[[英超|英超]]對[[曼城|曼城]]一戰首次上陣，在該仗他於60分鐘入替[[阿隆·拉姆塞|艾朗·藍斯]]。

2008年12月賀迪和阿仙奴簽下長約<small><ref name="contract"/></small>。2008年12月31日他被外借至[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]，直至2008/09球季完結<small><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.watfordfc.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10400~1504594,00.html |title=A new signing for a new year |work=Watfordfc.com |date=2009-01-06 |accessdate=2009-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216092802/http://www.watfordfc.com/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10400~1504594%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-02-16 }}</ref></small>，期間分別在聯賽及[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]上陣7場及3場。2009年10月9日被外借到[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]1個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/8297876.stm |title=Brighton snap up Arsenal's Hoyte |work=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-09 |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archive-date=2020-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421173150/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brighton/8297876.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，11月7日在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]對[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:韦康比流浪者;zh-hk:韋甘比}-]]時被罰一面[[紅牌|紅牌]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8341141.stm |title=Wycombe 4-4 Brighton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-07 |accessdate=2009-12-15 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106072613/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/8341141.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，需停賽3場，而他的借用期獲延長到2010年1月。借用期滿後他仍然留隊訓練，最終白禮頓成功獲阿仙奴應允延長借用直至球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5854134,00.html |title=Seagulls extend Hoyte deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-12 |accessdate=2010-01-13 |archive-date=2010-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100115083629/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5854134,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，期間合共為白禮頓在聯賽及盃賽上陣21場。

2010/11年球季賀迪繼續在阿仙奴預備隊上陣，於2010年10月29日被外借到[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[林肯城足球俱乐部|林肯城]]1個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/lincoln_city/9140222.stm |title=Lincoln City sign Gavin Hoyte & Ashley Grimes on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-10-29 |accessdate=2010-10-30 |archive-date=2010-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101101080208/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/lincoln_city/9140222.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣5場聯賽及1場[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]，獲延長借用至翌年1月29日<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.redimps.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10440~2230026,00.html |title=Hoyte Extends Youth Loan |publisher=[[林肯城足球俱乐部|''redimps.co.uk'']] |date=2010-11-25 |accessdate=2010-11-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101128081529/http://www.redimps.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10440~2230026%2C00.html |archivedate=2010-11-28 }}</ref>。2011年1月8日在[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]第二圈重賽對[[靴尔福特联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:靴尔福特; zh-hk:赫里福特聯;}-]]賽事初段傷出<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/9341902.stm |title=Lincoln City 3-4 Hereford |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-08 |accessdate=2011-02-23 |archive-date=2011-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110209074355/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/9341902.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因[[腿後腱|腿後腱]]受傷一度返回阿仙奴治理，傷癒後於1月31日重返林肯城，並獲延長借用至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.arsenal.com/news/reserves-news/hoyte-rejoins-lincoln-city-on-loan |title=Hoyte rejoins Lincoln City on loan |publisher=[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|''arsenal.com'']] |date=2011-01-31 |accessdate=2011-02-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110203034752/http://www.arsenal.com/news/reserves-news/hoyte-rejoins-lincoln-city-on-loan |archivedate=2011-02-03 }}</ref>。2011年2月19日主場對[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|車士打菲特]]開賽僅12分鐘便因傷退下火線，賽後證實[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]十字韌帶和膝內側副韌同告撕裂，需要接受[[手術|手術]]治理，預計將要缺陣6個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/lincoln_city/9413084.stm |title=Lincoln defender Hoyte's season ended by knee injury |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-03 |accessdate=2011-03-04 |archive-date=2011-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110304214258/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/lincoln_city/9413084.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

